  "texts": [
    "In the data preparation step, each photo's aspect is altered.",
    "Then, these images are split and augmented.",
    "Next, in the deep learning model formation and training, three pre-trained CNNs including AlexNet 52, ResNet50 53, and DenseNet201 54 are constructed and then retrained using the two CRC datasets.",
    "After that in the feature extraction and fusion, deep features are extracted from each CNN and then their dimension is reduced using DCT.",
    "Afterward, these features are fused using DCT, and their dimensions are further diminished using a Zigzag scanning algorithm."
